terraform-show: ### Show state - mandatory: STACK|STACKS|INFRASTRUCTURE_STACKS=[comma-separated names]; optional: PROFILE=[name],OPTS=[Terraform options, e.g. -json plan.out > build/automation/tmp/plan.out.json]
